item.description:
This is for beginners and veteran readers alike, I have worked with all levels. Bring any type of cards you like and as many questions as you can throw at me we will work out all the kinks and build your confidence and accuracy in a judgement free zone.

7-8pm

*no refunds will be offered. if I am given 24 hour notice you may use this towards another circle or event.
